<title>HONG KONG: RJP 15-month net loss HK$77.79 mln.</title>
<headline>RJP 15-month net loss HK$77.79 mln.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1996-11-25</dateline>
<text>
<p>Fifteen months ended June 30</p>
<p>(in million HK$ unless stated)</p>
<p>    Shr (H.K. cents)	   24.72 loss vs 53.29 loss (adjusted)</p>
<p>    Dividend (H.K. cents)    nil	  vs nil</p>
<p>    Exceptional items	  78.63 loss vs 37.57 loss</p>
<p>    Net			    77.79 loss vs 76.23 loss</p>
<p>    Turnover		     337.86     vs 255.51</p>
<p>    Company name		 RJP Electronics Ltd</p>
<p>    Books close		  December 16-23</p>
<p>    Dividend payable	   N/A</p>
<p>NOTE - RJP makes consumer electronic products.</p>
<p>The company changed its financial year-end to June 30 from March 31. Comparative figures are for 12 months ended March 31, 1995.</p>
<p>Net is after an exceptional loss on provision for stocks, bad debts and property under development, disposal of fixed assets and redundancy payment.</p>
<p>Comparative loss per share has been adjusted for the rights issue and consolidation of shares in 1996.</p>
<p>-- Hong Kong Newsroom (852) 843 6368</p>
